  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-01-24",
    "date": "2025-04-24T16:44:07Z",
    "text": "Universal Right To Vote by Mail Act of 2025\n\nThis bill expands voting by mail in federal elections.\n\nSpecifically, the bill prohibits states from imposing on eligible voters additional conditions or requirements to cast ballots by mail in federal elections, except states may impose a deadline for requesting the ballot and related voting materials and for returning a ballot.\n\nThe bill also requires states to provide individuals with notice and opportunity to cure discrepancies or defects with their absentee or mail-in ballots."
  },
